Package es.uam.eps.ir.relison.grid.diffusion.filter

Class FilterParameterReader

java.lang.Object
es.uam.eps.ir.relison.grid.ParametersReader
es.uam.eps.ir.relison.grid.diffusion.filter.FilterParameterReader
public class FilterParameterReader
extends ParametersReader
Class for reading a filter for information diffusion. For each filter, a single set of parameters is read.
File format:
filter:
param1: ...
Author:
Javier Sanz-Cruzado (javier.sanz-cruzado@uam.es), Pablo Castells (pablo.castells@uam.es)
See Also:
